Les tubes doivent être de taille raisonnable<ref>{{en}}[http://www.ecoduna.com/pages/en/mainsite/technology.php?lang=EN Ecoduna algae technology]</ref>.

Exemple matériel libre :
* Tubes transparents verticaux<ref>{{en}}[http://algaegeek.com/Projects/Photo-Bio-reactor-V2/ Simple Photo Bio Reactor Array V.2 ]</ref>{{,}}<ref>{{en}}[http://algaegeek.com/Projects/Photo-Bio-Reactor-V1/ Simple Photo Bio Reactor Array V.1 ]</ref>.
